OL,3,CCovid Inquiry: intensive care units
OL,4,Cwere a 'scene from hell' during
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,FEngland's Chief Medical Officer,
OL,8,FProfessor Sir Chris Whitty, told the
OL,9,Finquiry that England entered the
OL,10,Fpandemic with a lower number of
OL,11,Fintensive care beds than other
OL,12,Fdeveloped countries, as Rebecca Barry
OL,13,Freports
OL,15,FSick patients "rained from the sky"
OL,16,Fand nurses were forced to use plastic
OL,17,Fsacks with cable ties as makeshift
OL,18,Fbody bags during the height of the
OL,19,Fpandemic, the Covid inquiry has heard.
