OL,3,CCovid Inquiry: intensive care units
OL,4,Cwere a 'scene from hell' during
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,F"Sometimes (staff) were so overwhelmed
OL,8,Fthat they were putting patients in
OL,9,Fbody bags, lifting them from the bed,
OL,10,Fputting them on the floor, and putting
OL,11,Fanother patient in that bed straight
OL,12,Faway because there wasn't time,"
OL,13,FProfessor Kevin Fong, a former
OL,14,Fnational clinical adviser in emergency
OL,15,Fpreparedness, resilience and response
OL,16,Fat NHS England told the inquiry.
OL,18,FHe broke down in tears as he described
OL,19,Fthe "scene from hell" in the intensive
OL,20,Fcare units during the Covid pandemic.
