OL,7,F"They're no strangers to death; but
OL,8,Fthe scale of death was truly, truly
OL,9,Fastounding," Professor Kevin Fong said.
OL,11,F"Those nurses talk about being really
OL,12,Ftraumatised by that, because they had
OL,13,Frecurring nightmares
OL,15,Fabout feeling like they were just
OL,16,Fthrowing bodies away.
OL,18,F"We had nurses talking about patients
OL,19,Fraining from the sky."
