OL,12,FThe inquiry heard many hospitals ran
OL,13,Fout of body bags and other equipment
OL,14,Fand that hospitals were so short-
OL,15,Fstaffed, some nurses were forced to
OL,16,Fwear adult nappies, as they had no
OL,17,Ftime for toilet breaks.
OL,19,FOthers bought their own protective
OL,20,Fequipment from hardware shops.
