OL,7,FIn some hospitals, the inquiry heard
OL,8,Fstaff only wore underwear underneath
OL,9,Ftheir gowns because there were no
OL,10,Fscrubs available.
OL,12,FEngland's Chief Medical Officer,
OL,13,FProfessor Sir Chris Whitty, told the
OL,14,Finquiry that England entered the
OL,15,Fpandemic with a lower number of
OL,16,Fintensive care beds than other
OL,17,Fdeveloped countries.
OL,19,F"Now that's a choice, that's a
OL,20,Fpolitical choice," he said.
