OL,7,F"It's a system configuration choice,
OL,8,Fbut it is a choice.
OL,10,F"Therefore, you have less reserve when
OL,11,Fa major emergency happens, even if
OL,12,Fit's short of something of the scale
OL,13,Fof Covid."
OL,15,FAbout 227,000 people died in the UK
OL,16,Ffrom Covid between March 2020 and May
OL,17,F2023.
