OL,7,FIn his evidence to the inquiry,
OL,8,FProfessor Kevin Fong said what he saw
OL,9,Fin the Intensive Care Units every day
OL,10,Fduring the Covid pandemic was far
OL,11,Fworse than the aftermath of the Soho
OL,12,Fbombing in 1999 and the July 7 London
OL,13,Fbombings.
OL,15,F"The intensive care unit was full.
OL,16,FTheir overflow areas were full, their
OL,17,Fnon-invasive ventilation unit, their
OL,18,Frespiratory unit was full," he said.
